title: Brand New 3-Bedrooms Apartment in Cypress Hills
posting_body: ['Brand new gut renovated 3 bedroom apartment for rent in prime Cypress Hills Brooklyn.', 'This spacious 2nd floor unit is completely renovated with custom granite kitchen counter tops, stainless steel appliances and hardwood floors.', 'The master is large and amazingly bright with two oversized windows.', 'The living room boosts high ceiling and hard wood floors.', ' Close to all transportation.', 'Only blocks away from J/Z Train station at Crescent Street.', 'Close to Jackie Robinson Parkway.', ' Nearby you will find various restaurants, pizzerias, banks, Deli/supermarkets, laundromats.', 'The property is ready for immediate occupancy.', ' Proof of income and background check are required.', 'For more information, please email me your PHONE Number, your full name, who is going to move in, and a brief description of yourself.', 'I will get back to you ASAP.', 'Thanks.']
